summary: This is a remake of Legend of Zelda Twilight Princess\\\' whole game, I will be adding quests later.
descriptionHtml:
This is a remake of Legend of Zelda Twilight Princess\' whole map.
It\'s going slow right now because I\'m still learning the basics of the construction kit, I will be working on this everyday because I have no life xD and I wanted to have this done.

This is FAR from done but i needed a backup in case my computer decided to do some thing bad and delete it. (I don\'t know I\'m paranoid) 

Under Heavy Construction about 0.1% done.......

If you really want to see my progress just type \"coc wilderness\" in the console after pressing the ~ button.

I will update my progress everyday so you guys know my progress, I will work on making an entrance from somewhere but that is still out of my knowledge in the creation kit.
author: RobertRyan
